            <event type="researchStep">
               <head type="stepTitle" xml:lang="en">Describe measurement. Measurement / Spectra
            acquisition / Storage of data and metadata files</head>
               <desc type="definition" xml:lang="en">
                  <p>Recording of the FTIR spectra taken on
              representative sites on the CH object. First evaluation of the spectrum (assessment of
              FTIR peaks and eventually distortions). The measurement conditions (number of scans,
              acquisition specral range, spectral resolution) are documented in a text file for all
              the measurements or in form of metadata file for each spectrum file.</p>
                  <p>The position of the instrument must be kept as fixed as possible to avoid artefacts
              and data rejection by the processing system.</p>
               </desc>
               <desc xml:lang="en" type="terms">
                  <term type="standard" key="ASCII"/>
